291
00:17:26,233 --> 00:17:28,300
Guan Xi, eh?

292
00:17:28,367 --> 00:17:29,700
Già.

293
00:17:31,500 --> 00:17:33,300
Ecco che arriva la tua, fratello.

294
00:17:33,367 --> 00:17:35,167
Benvenuto a Hong Kong.

295
00:17:35,233 --> 00:17:36,567
Piacere di conoscerti, sono

296
00:17:46,833 --> 00:17:48,567
Hey, Gary.

297
00:17:48,633 --> 00:17:51,100
Hey, Conner. Ho quello che ti serve.

298
00:17:51,167 --> 00:17:54,567
Ottimo. Se potessi darmi solo la "P e la L"

